name: ELEFANCLUB 05
description:
An original illustration for ALL collectors (1+) of Les Elefants Terribles.

“This is a rock n roll creation,
so gimme peanut danger 
in sin sin atty butter. 

There’s ice-cream fat on your bod,
so south by little sunswine 
puke paint that dyed milk.

You are what you read,
poor have-a-cuc’s 
emaciated pup.

Jim as Andy saves the day,  
the beetle burden 
of April 23.

The praying couple on a loaf,
on a bust 
to be consumed.”

Rotring pen and markers on paper

By Guillaume Cornet and Only Child No Pets
Follow @elefants_tez on twitter
